Support for iOS 15 and watchOS 8. Improved the transcription process. Hear VoiceOver through a headset while recording from the internal mic. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Added a button to skip forward IAP . Added the option to adjust the speed of saved audio IAP . Fixed problem with auto splitting. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Faster app startup 0.52 seconds faster on iPhone 6 . Fixed problem with auto send. Fixed problem when changing the recording quality. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.
Fixed problem with auto splitting. Memos in the trash can are now deleted after 30 days. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Use a widget to quickly start recording. Automatic transcription of memos¹. Stereo recording using the builtin microphones². Directly view progress of downloads uploads and compressions. Rename memos on Apple Watch. Add position markers while recording on Apple Watch¹. Memos are compressed while recording¹. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update. ¹ Requires an active subscription. ² Requires a compatible device and an active Pro subscription.

Send memos by email without size restrictions except the ones from email providers . Improved connections with https: imesart.com connect.php. More space for list of memos on iPad. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.
